    "comment": "Synthetic restart-action fixture for the Nokia BGW320-505. Drives the form_md5_nonce action-auth login (GET+POST /cgi-bin/login.ha) followed by the nonce-injected reboot (GET+POST /cgi-bin/restart.ha). All values are sanitized placeholders; no real access code, nonce, or session token is present.",
