            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head><title>Restart Device</title></head>\n<body>\n<div id=\"content-sub\">\n<h1>Restart Device</h1>\n<p>Restarting the device will interrupt your connection for several minutes.</p>\n<form method=\"post\" action=\"/cgi-bin/restart.ha\" name=\"restartform\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"nonce\" value=\"REDACTED_RESTART_NONCE\" />\n<input type=\"submit\" name=\"Restart\" value=\"Restart\" class=\"cssbtn\" />\n</form>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
